    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-09-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-09-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="607"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d607">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.48/522</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Russian Embassy</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Department of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Memorandum</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Russian Government is informed that the Polish General Committee in
                    Switzerland has applied to the United States Government in order to ask
                    immediate help for the starving population of Poland, on the same basis as the
                    assistance rendered to Belgium.</p>
                <p>The Russian Government is supporting that petition of the Poles emphasizing the
                    distressing conditions in Poland and the desirability of giving aid as soon as
                    possible.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-09-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 5, 1917</hi>
                        </date>. <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received September 6.</hi>]</dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
